# Cargo feature flags for building zallet in the zcash/integration-tests CI.
#
# The integration RPC suite runs in regtest, which the default `zebra-state`
# chain backend does not support, so the Zaino backend is pinned here. The
# integration-tests build step reads this file, ignores comment lines (`#`),
# and passes the remaining tokens verbatim to `cargo build` (appending any
# platform-specific features, such as `zcashd-import`, on its side).
#
# Tracking: zebra-state regtest support — zcash/wallet#495.
--no-default-features --features zaino
